For favicon

<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="favicon.svg">

| Collection | Created when |
|---|---|
| `courses/{id}` | Admin creates a new course |
| `courses/{id}/nominations/{email}` | Admin nominates a user to a course |
| `exams/{id}` | Admin creates an exam in sf-certs-hub |
| `exams/{id}/nominations/{email}` | Admin nominates a learner to an exam |
| `examSlots` | Learner schedules an exam slot |
| `examSessions` | Learner begins exam setup (Begin Setup flow) |
| `examResults/{uid}` | Learner completes or times out of an exam |
| `progress/{uid}` | Learner passes an exam |
| `notifications/{email}/items` | App fires any notification event |
| `auditLog` | Admin or proctor performs a privileged action |
| `rescheduleRequests` | Learner submits a reschedule request |
| `proctorReassignmentRequests` | Admin reassigns a proctor to a slot |
| `reviewerSessions/{uid}/{courseSlug}/{moduleId}` | Reviewer begins reviewing a module |
| `adminConfig/githubPAT` | Manually created once — stores the GitHub PAT |
